# AI Chatbot in Java

This project is a simple GUI-based chatbot built with Java Swing.

## Features
- Simple chat window
- User input text field
- Send button
- Basic keyword-based responses

## Requirements
- Java JDK installed on your computer

## How to Run
1. Open a terminal in the project folder.
2. Compile the program:
   ```bash
   javac chatbot.java
   ```
3. Run the program:
   ```bash
   java chatbot
   ```

## Example Questions
- hello
- hi
- how are you
- your name
- bye
- java
- ai

## Notes
This is a basic chatbot and does not use a real AI API yet. It responds using predefined rules.
